# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

REMOVE_BACKGROUND - Recipe for removing a background from images

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A simple PICARD recipe to fit and remove a background from an image.

=head1 NOTES

The images should not be of extended sources.

This primitive creates an output file for each input file with a
suffix <_back> which will replace the existing suffix.

=head1 DISPLAY

No display is used by this recipe.

